         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Sydney bot. Garden 12 April 57 ¶ My dear Sir William ¶  ¶ The supplementary mail for Europe is just closing. Yesterday I forwarded to you a long letter containing I think some bot. information not wit...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">57.04.11</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To William Hooker</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RBG Kew, Directors' letters, vol. LXXIV, Australia letters 1851-8, letter no. 160. </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS address: 'Sir William Jackson Hooker, K.H., D.C.L., F.H.S., V.P.L.S. &amp;c &amp;c &amp;c, Director of the Royal Gardens of <seg style="">
                        <hi rend="underline">Kew</hi>
                     </seg> near London.'</p>
               </note>Sydney bot. Garden 12 April 57<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">The MS of this letter is postmarked Sydney, 11 April 1857.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Sir William</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The supplementary mail for Europe is just closing. Yesterday I forwarded to you a long letter containing I think some bot. information not without value to you.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to W. Hooker, 6 April 1857.</p>
               </note> I transmitted also diagn of <name key="Dennisonia">Dennisonia</name>, <name key="Barklya">Barklya</name> &amp; <name key="Laboucheria">Laboucheria</name>
               <note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">M erected <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                        <name key="Dennisonia">Dennisonia</name> (D. ternifolia)</seg>, <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                        <name key="Barklya">Barklya</name> (B. syringifolia) </seg>and<seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                        <name key="Laboucheria">Laboucheria</name> (L. chlorostachya)</seg> (B59.02.02, pp. 158-9), in honour respectively of the Governors of Vic and NSW and the Secretary of State for the Colonies, London.</p>
               </note> with specimens. Please let me know by a few lines the reciept of the letter, so that if its contents do not reach you I may make up for it again.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have Mr Gregorys offic. acknowledgement in hand, stating that I bestowed all possible care on packing the plants.<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See A. Gregory to M, 8 April 1857.</p>
               </note> The loss has made me quite ill, and I am afraid I do not possess sufficient Newtonian philosophy to get easily over it. How a number of people who had on board of the vessel actually nothing to do, but to watch for the safety of the property of the Government, were unable (by the absence of damage to the vessel) to keep the few important things of the expedition dry, is quite beyond my comprehension.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Ever your most attached</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">I have a new genus of <name key="Pontederiaceae">Pontederiaceae</name>! The order is I believe unkown from Australia. It has regular [flowers].<note xml:id="ftn6" type="footnote" n="6">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Presumably<seg style="font-style: italic; "> Limnostachys</seg> (<seg style="font-style: italic; ">L. cyanea</seg>) (B58.03.01, p. 24).</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Barklya">Barklya</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Dennisonia">Dennisonia</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Laboucheria">Laboucheria</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Pontederiaceae">Pontederiaceae</name>
            </p>
